deck: An American actor and voice actor.
description:
Comic Related Roles

Moore voiced Victor Stone/Cyborg in the Justice League: War animated film. He will reprise his role in the sequel, Justice League: Throne of Atlantis.
name: Shemar Moore

description:
Comic Related Roles

Gorham voiced Barry Allen/The Flash in the Justice League: War animated film. He will also reprise his role in the sequel, Justice League: Throne of Atlantis.
name: Christopher Gorham

deck: An American actor and voice actor.
description: Sean Astin voices Shazam in the DC animated movie Justice League: War. He rose to fame playing Mikey in Steven Spielberg's The Goonies, he is most famous for playing Samwise Gamgee in The Lord Of The Rings Trilogy and voices Raphael in the TV series Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
name: Sean Astin

deck: Comic book artist most known for making Saturday Morning Cereal comics.
name: Zach Weinersmith

deck: An American film director, screenwriter and producer, James decided to pursue a career in the arts after 12 months with the U.S. Army in Iraq. James is an outspoken conservative and very active in politics. A native of Tucson, James' next work is a Western, Up The Trail.
name: James A. Bretney

deck: A gifted European Designer, Slawomir is the creative genius behind The Kursk's impactful covers. He has applied his diverse talents to music (under the label Northland Music Productions), visual design, photography and of course, graphic novels.
name: Slawomir Nietupski

deck: An actor who grew up in Minsk, Belarus, Sasha graduated from the literature department of the Silesian University in Poland. He has performed with Queensland Theatre Company. The Kursk was his first published play.
name: Sasha Janowicz

deck: A native of Colombia residing in New Jersey, Andrea is inspired by fantasy, families, foreign cultures and World history. The recipient of several awards, Andrea has also illustrated children's books such as Ben the Raindrop and Canon's Birthday.
name: Andrea Montano

deck: Born in St. Louis, Missouri, Jeery Thompson has garnered success in a wide range of media: Short and feature lms, music, art and comic books. He has a slew of lms in development, all the while working on his musical ventures. An entrepreneur, Thompson has scored a partnership with the upstart company, Inkkas.
name: Jeffery Thompson

deck: Aaron Foster is an artist who sees the world as shapes and colors, full of possibilities. Throughout his life, Aaron has worked diligently to develop his love of art and animation. Currently, he holds a degree as Master of Arts. Aaron resides in Dallas, TX., where he serves clients as an artist, illustrator and graphic designer.
name: Aaron Foster
